ANETAC — Arabic Named Entity Transliteration and Classification
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Files:    internal/data/anetac/{train,dev,test}.{ar,en}
Source:   https://github.com/HadjAmeur/ANETAC-Dataset
License:  MIT

The Arabic dictionary used by the default Transliterator is built from the
train/dev/test splits of the ANETAC corpus (~80k Arabic named entities paired
with their English transliterations).

